<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" 
	      xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">
  
    <Paragraph>
        The following samples demonstrate the different kinds of Cell Types present in the GridControl.
    </Paragraph>

	 <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Basic Cell Type</Bold>- This sample showcases the Basic Cell Types.
    </Paragraph>
	
    <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Combo Box</Bold>- This sample illustrates binding an ItemsSource or a string collection to a combo box. It also illustrates binding a foreign-key reference through a drop-down list control.
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Currency Cell</Bold>- This sample illustrates the use of a currency editor in the GridControl.
    </Paragraph>
	
    <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Custom Drop Down </Bold>- This sample illustrates how to create a custom Drop-Down Control.
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Data Template Cell </Bold>- This sample illustrates using Data Templates as cell types in the GridControl.
    </Paragraph>
	
	 <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Custom Data Template Cell </Bold>- This sample illustrates Custom Data Templates as cell types in the GridControl.
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Date-Time Cell </Bold>- This sample illustrates the use of a Date-Time editor inside the GridControl.
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14">
        <Bold>Double Edit Cell Demo</Bold> - This sample illustrates the use of a Double Editor in the GridControl.
    </Paragraph>
	
    <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Integer Edit Cell </Bold> - This sample illustrates the use of an Integer Editor in the GridControl.
    </Paragraph>
	
    <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Mask Edit Cell </Bold> - This sample illustrates the use of a Mask Editor in the GridControl.
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Nested Grid </Bold> - This sample illustrates the use of a Nested Grid inside the GridControl.
    </Paragraph>
	
    <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Percent Edit Cell </Bold> - This sample illustrates the use of a Percent Editor in the GridControl.
    </Paragraph>
	
	<Paragraph>
        <Bold>Rich TextBox Cell Type Demo</Bold>- This sample illustrates the usage of Rich TextBox and Image Cells in the GridControl.
    </Paragraph>
	
    <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Up Down Cell </Bold> - This sample illustrates the use of an Up-Down Editor in the GridControl.
    </Paragraph>
	
	<Paragraph>
        <Bold>TextImage Cell </Bold> - This sample illustrates how to display Image in Grid cells along with the text.
    </Paragraph>
	
   <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Gauge Chart </Bold>- This sample illustrates the usage of Charts and Gauges showcased in a dashboard with a GridControl.
    </Paragraph>

   <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Advanced DataTemplate Cell </Bold>- This sample simulates a Advanced DataTemplate Cell Demo application by using custom cell types.
    </Paragraph>
	
</FlowDocument>
